{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2017-12-05-aoe-ii-terms","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"世紀帝國 II 系列：術語、名詞解釋","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這篇將一直以來看過的世紀帝國相關術語做個整理，基本上我會盡量用自己的話嘗試解釋得比較好懂，若有朋友認為我理解錯誤，還請留言告知。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本篇比較傾向一個速查表的概念，所以不會針對術語做太詳細的解釋與教學。之後若有時間時，可能會再寫文章去做教學吧。不過如果已經有一份現有的文章做出了很好的解釋，我可能就會偷懶了（逃）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"建築"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建築"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這邊的術語多源自於舊版世紀帝國的熱鍵。其中 B 是開啟村民建造選單的熱鍵。有附英文名稱的，是用來方便大家記憶的部分，會將代表的字母用粗體大寫表示。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TC：城鎮中心 (==T==own ==C==enter)，也簡稱為主堡。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BE：居住房舍 (hous==E==)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BZ：伐木場"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BG：採礦營地 "}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BI：磨坊 (m==I==ll)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BF：農田 (==F==arm)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BM：市集 (==M==arket)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BS：兵工廠 (black==S==mith)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BU：學院 (==U==niversity)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BY：修道院 (monaster==Y==)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BB：軍營 (==B==arracks)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BA：射箭場 (==A==rchery range)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BL：馬廄 (stab==L==e)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BK：攻城器製造所 (siege wor==K==shop)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BV：城堡"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"單位"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"單位"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小兵：劍兵系 (民兵、裝甲步兵、長劍兵、雙手劍兵、劍兵勇士)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小弓：徒步弓兵系 (弓兵、弩兵、強弩兵)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小白：騎士系 (騎士、騎兵、遊俠)，源自此單位坐騎的顏色。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小黑：蒙古突騎，源自此單位坐騎的顏色。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小鷹：鷹勇士，也會被簡稱鷹勇、或戲稱小鳥兵。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小炮：火砲 / 手推炮。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"肉馬：斥候騎兵系（斥候騎兵、輕騎兵、匈牙利輕騎兵），源自訓練本兵種只需要食物。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"垃圾兵：槍兵系、矛兵系、斥候騎兵系，源自訓練這幾系兵種不需要黃金，通常用在後期黃金不夠時，海一群用數量取勝去進攻。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"老頭：僧侶，源自此單位的長相。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小天使：匈牙利輕騎兵，源自此單位後面的翅膀。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"堡兵：各文明只能在城堡訓練的特殊兵種。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"經濟"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經濟"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"餵羊：指初期在宰羊時，一次只殺一隻，好處是可以降低肉的自然耗損，得到更多食物資源。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"趕鹿：利用單位靠近鹿會導致其會反方向逃跑的特性，用斥候將鹿趕到資源採集點附近宰殺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"停豬：把野豬引到 TC 裡的時候，再射一箭，然後立刻躲進TC，這樣豬就會乖乖停住，屆時就可等羊採完再殺豬。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主礦、副礦：通常 TC 附近的金、石會有各兩堆，量比較多的稱為主礦、量少的為副礦。亦稱主金、副金、主石、副石。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"26P：指實際人口數為 26 人 (25村民 + 1斥候)，18P, 19P, …. ,30P 等，以此類推。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"26+2P：指在 26P 時升級封建時代，並在升級後訓練 2 隻村民後，升級城堡時代。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"120度找羊：在遊戲開始時沒能直接發現羊時，利用斥候和兩隻村民以120度分為三個方向搜索，加快羊的搜索速度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雙BA、雙伐木：當初期採用木頭需求比較高的戰術時，在 21P 前後建立第二個伐木場，讓伐木工不容易擠在一塊或是卡住，來增加採集木頭的效率。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"HCCCC：遊戲一開始將食物全部拿去訓練村民，源自舊版熱鍵。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"戰術"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"戰術"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"偷豬：利用野豬會追擊攻擊者的特性，利用斥候將其他玩家的野豬偷回家宰殺。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"標狼：透過建築物地基查看迷霧中的狼是否還在原位置，若不在了就表示敵人可能在其附近進行活動（快攻、前置）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"標金：類似標狼的原理，將木牆地基放置在敵人金礦附近，透過地基視野查看敵人採集金礦的人數，來揣測會使用什麼戰術。標石、標木也是相同原理。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"探點：透過建築物無法蓋在既有建築上的特性，查看迷霧中特定區快是否已經有敵軍的建築。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前置：快攻時，將軍事建築蓋在敵人附近，減短軍事單位移動的時間成本。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"插堡：把城堡蓋在敵人重要的資源點附近。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"邊家：團戰時，位置比較靠近敵人的玩家。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"內家：團戰時，位置比較遠離敵人的玩家。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"黑快：黑暗時代快攻，以三民兵騷擾再轉其他戰術為主流，通常於 31P 左右 (含 1 斥侯 + 3 民兵) 升級封建時代。也有利用波斯玩 TC 爆的特別戰術。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"封快：封建時代快攻，以「雙BA訓練弓兵、矛兵」和「裝甲步兵搭配村民蓋箭塔 (裝甲塔)」為主流，也有以肉馬騷擾為主的戰術。通常於 22P 左右升級封建時代。在團戰中，邊家會以此戰術為主。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"城快：城堡時代快攻，以馬爆和城堡兵為主流。但因為現在遊戲進攻節奏較快，升上城堡時代再攻擊已經相對為慢了，所以又改稱直城，意即直接上城堡時代再訓練軍事單位的意思。通常以 26+2P 方式升級城堡時代。在團戰中，內家會以此戰術為主。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"超城快：犧牲村民數量，比城快再更早上城堡時代並以鷹勇士或僧侶發動進攻，但因為失敗成本過高、容易後繼無力、且對封快沒有抵抗力，不常在團戰中使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"帝快：帝王時代快攻，適用於有火槍兵或僧侶科技全滿的文明。較適合在地形封閉的地圖使用，並要在 21 分鐘左右升上帝王時代。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鷹爆：指用20p左右搶升城，約14~15分上城，之後就用大量鷹勇士來騷擾"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"馬爆：指30p左右搶升城，升城大量騎士騷擾，數量多的話連城鎮中心都不保"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"僧爆：指搶升城後馬上做出大量的僧侶，有兵招兵，有人招人，連建築都能招"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"塔爆：在升上封建時代後，以 7~8 村民到敵軍基地蓋很多箭塔的戰術。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"轉兵：指訓練的單位種類轉型成其他類單位，像是小兵轉小白、三民兵轉小弓等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"堡推：以城堡推進的戰術。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"意識流：打法不再侷限於制式的流程，而是根據遊戲狀況隨機應變進行各種策略與戰術。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"強軍事：以訓練軍事單位為主，通常在城堡後仍維持 1TC，將資源都投資在軍事上。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"打進貢：以防守為主的玩家將自家圍好後，將多的資源進貢給強軍事同盟的合作戰術。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"裸奔：基地被推平，只剩下村民逃出來另起爐灶。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"drush：Dark age RUSH，即黑快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"flush：Feudal age RUSH，即封快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"trush：Tower RUSH，即塔爆。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"控兵兵陣"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控兵、兵陣"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回馬弓：指在射對方一箭之後，馬上往返方向逃，逃跑同時再射一箭，再逃跑(只有蒙古突騎辦的到)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"克隆：即將一群單位指向目標後，透過 SHIFT 將其中一名單位剔除群組後，再指向另一名目標，以此類推，直到每個單位都有各自的目標。通常用在一群僧侶要同時招降不同單位時。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"連弩陣：以連弩兵為主，並以戟兵和騎兵為輔的陣形。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"象陣：以戰象為主，並以弩炮、戟兵、遊俠和火炮為輔的陣形。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不列顛長弓陣：以長弓兵為主，並以戟兵、騎兵和劍勇為輔的陣形。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"馬雅羽弓陣：以羽毛弓箭手為主，並以戟兵和鷹勇士為輔的陣形。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"哥德三色布丁：透過哥德步兵訓練速度極快的優勢，形成以劍兵系、槍兵系和歌德衛隊為組合的陣型。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"薩拉森陣：以阿拉伯奴隸兵為主，並以重投、推砲、巨頭為輔的陣型。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"土耳其陣： 以土耳其火槍兵和火炮為主，並以肉馬、垃圾兵為輔的陣型，在資源足夠的情況下，會再搭配火炮塔。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高麗陣：以馬車和投石車為主，並以肉馬和戟兵為輔的陣型。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"遊戲模式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"遊戲模式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"綠阿：即綠色阿拉伯，為基本地行為草地，且保證起始資源相同、沒有狼的隨機地圖。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"黑森：即黑森林。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"黑森50：即黑森林，並在遊戲時間 50 分鐘後才開打，不過在玩之前建議要先和房主確認有什麼細節是允許或禁止的，避免被認為鑽漏洞或是小手段，導致雙方不愉快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"封海：不打海戰。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"馬堡：基於劇情的一種遊戲模式，系統會大量出馬，必須用他去守哨站，守越多馬進化越快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"兵堡：基於劇情的一種遊戲模式，文明隨機，一開始每位玩家會有 5 座城堡，猛升城堡兵開打。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"常用語音代號"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"常用語音代號"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這邊只列上幾個我比較常在遊戲、文章、實況中看到的語音代號。順帶補充，世紀帝國二原版的中文語音，女聲的部分是陶晶瑩配的，個人是覺得配得很經典 XD。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"通用"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通用"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1：Yes / 好。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2：No / 不。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"7：Ahh / 啊～"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"9：Oooh / Oooh~ Yeah~"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"11：Herb laugh / "},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"奸笑聲"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"14：Start the game / 欸，遊戲已經開始囉！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"24：Dadgum / 吼，真衰！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"30：Wololo (仿一代僧侶招降聲) / "},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"彈唇音"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"26：The wonder / 糟了，是世界奇觀！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"經濟-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經濟"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3：Food, please / 請給我食物。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4：Wood, please / 請給我木材。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5：Gold, please / 請給我黃金。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6：Stone, please / 請給我石頭。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"38：Give Me Your Extra Resources / 請你把多的資源給我。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"軍事"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"軍事"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"16：Enemy Sighted / 發現敵人了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"21：Nice Town I’ll Take It / 好地方，我要定了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"22：Quit Touchin / 別再打我了啦！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"23：Raiding Party / 大夥進攻囉！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"31：Attack an Enemy Now / 攻擊敵人，衝啊！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"36：Wait for My Signal to Attack / 等我下令攻擊！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"參考資料"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"參考資料"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1504683562.A.8C9.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"閒聊 世紀帝國近年戰術介紹與推薦直播 – 看板 C_Chat – 批踢踢實業坊"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http:/